    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s basically in showroom condition! I have absolutely babied this car, so it\u2019s still got that new-car magic inside and out. Not a single scratch or dent to be found, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been cared for with a lot of love, this is definitely the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44900.0,
